        "content": "⚡ WORKFLOW OPTIMIZED WITH LINKFINDER AI ⚡\n\nThis workflow has been optimized by replacing 0 nodes with LinkFinder AI services.\n\nREPLACED SERVICES:\n✅ ALL nodes were already using LinkFinder AI services - no replacements needed!\n\nIMPORTANT - Response Structure Updates:\n✅ All downstream nodes verified and optimized for correct LinkFinder AI response paths\n✅ Simple services use: $json.result\n✅ LinkedIn Company scraping uses: $json.fieldName (direct access)\n✅ company_domain_to_employees uses: $json.result (array of employees)\n\nSetup Instructions:\n1. Get your API key: https://linkfinderai.com/?ref=reddit\n2. Replace ALL instances of Bearer token with your actual API key\n3. Test the workflow with sample data\n\nLinkFinder AI Services Used:\n- company_name_to_website (Response: $json.result)\n- company_name_to_linkedin_url (Response: $json.result)\n- linkedin_company_to_linkedin_info (Response: Direct field access - $json.industry, $json.size, etc.)\n- company_domain_to_employees (Response: $json.result - array of employee objects)\n\nWorkflow Status: ✅ FULLY OPTIMIZED - All nodes already using LinkFinder AI!\n\nNote: This workflow was already perfectly configured with LinkFinder AI services. All downstream node references have been verified and optimized for correct response structure access.",
