    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔍 Company Decision Makers Enrichment Pipeline\n\n**What it does:** Takes a list of company names from Google Sheets, enriches each with website and LinkedIn data, then extracts key decision makers (Directors, VPs, C-level) for targeted outreach.\n\n**Input:** Google Sheet with column 'company_name' containing company names\n\n**Output:** Google Sheet with enriched company data + decision makers (name, title, email, LinkedIn, company info)\n\n**Scalability:** Processes companies in batches of 10 with 2-second delays to avoid rate limits\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Get API key from https://linkfinderai.com/?ref=reddit\n2. Replace Bearer token in all LinkFinder AI nodes with your actual API key\n3. Connect your Google account and configure Sheet IDs\n4. Set input sheet with company names in column A\n5. Create output sheet with headers: Company, Website, LinkedIn URL, Industry, Size, Employee Name, Employee Title, Employee Email, Employee LinkedIn\n\n**Services used:**\n- company_name_to_website (Response: $json.result)\n- company_name_to_linkedin_url (Response: $json.result)\n- linkedin_company_to_linkedin_info (Response: Direct fields - $json.industry, $json.size)\n- company_domain_to_employees (Response: $json.result array)\n\n**Perfect for:** Sales teams building targeted prospect lists, ABM campaigns, executive outreach programs",
        "height": 580,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 4
      },
